summary:
Enthusiastic native Italian with fluency in English, with 10+ years of work experience in customer service (b2c-b2b), inside sale and project management support assistant.
I have strong interpersonal and communication skills, flexibility and creativity to find solutions, out of the box mentality.
Immediately available, open to full-time, part-time, remote, opportunity in Customer Service, Inside Sales and Project Assistent.
